<h4 id="patriotism-and-nationalism">Patriotism and Nationalism</h4>
<ol>
  <li>patriotism: love that people feel for their country.</li>
  <li>nationalism: A desire by a large group of people(such as people who share the
same culture, history, language) to form a separate and independent nation of
their own.</li>
</ol>

